{
  "stem": "15962.7",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we don't know the English language properly, nor any math or chemistry.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they were feeding us all of this to catch up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In fact, the first year, because of the tremendous influx of veterans that could go to universities, we were shipped to a-- outside Montreal to an old air force base to-- to take classes, which was somewhat reminiscent of the army barracks.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well, they were army barracks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went two years.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then the next year, I moved back to Montreal.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I lived with some very kind people who just were interested to helping Jewish refugees.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were a Jewish family, very cultured.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was a lawyer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she was a musician.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were very nice to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it happened to be on the same street that my Czech friends lived.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I had some advantage there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was very much absorbed with learning, with studying.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was very enthusiastic about my studies.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that's what kept me going and thinking about other things.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I was not at all in touch with any refugees or any contemporary-- you know, that group of boys.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Didn't know of any.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so my thoughts were mostly on my studies.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And after almost three years, the visa came through, just in the middle of the summer.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I decided to have a summer job first in British Colombia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then, just before the year started, I went to the States without being assured that I would be accepted to university.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But fortunately, the day I crossed the border at Rouses Point, I got a telegram from Columbia that they had an opening and accepted me.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So, again, that was a question of good luck, because I didn't-- didn't apply to any other place.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
